investment. We seek fairer terms of international trade. We insist
that Africa is not perpetually relegated to being a dumping ground
for sub-standard goods coming from Europe or anywhere else," he
said.
</P>
<P>
African countries have pressed for the EU countries'
cancellation or rescheduling of their debt, but the countries have
refused to discuss the details of the issue at the ongoing summit.
</P>
<P>
