the figure is also an estimate because the exact extent of the
damage is still being quantified.
</P>
<P>
He said responses from the provinces to the disasters have been
 improving since January and the rescue missions are becoming
better organized.
</P>
<P>
The South African government will give its utmost support to
the flood- stricken provinces to develop disaster management
policies and health ministers from the affected countries in
southern Africa are co-ordinating efforts to combat the malaria
risk following the floods, Titus added. 
