globalization of military cooperation will be part of the
bilateral cooperation, which will pave the way for the
establishment of an effective relationship on defense, in the
ambit of the Portuguese-speaking countries.
</P>
<P>
According to the communique, the two sides will meet in Lisbon
in November over the approval of the technical military
cooperation program for the biennium 2001-2002. 
