said Tuesday that changes in the Cabinet will take effect on April
15,when Press Secretary Rodolfo Reyes leaves his post.
</P>
<P>
Speaking to reporters in the presidential palace, Estrada said
former broadcast executive, lawyer Ricardo Puno, will take over
Reyes' position on that date while Reyes will be appointed to head
the Manila Economic Cultural Office (MECO) in China's Taiwan.
</P>
