<HEADLINE> NPC Should Play Active Role, Li Peng (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
At the present time, the world's information industry is
witnessing extremely rapid growth. Shanghai should seize the
opportunity and do its utmost in technical development, products
upgrading, and personal training, Li said.
</P>
<P>
During his visit to the headquarters of the Standing Committee
of the Shanghai Municipal People's Congress, Li spoke highly of
the achievements made by the Municipal People's Congress in legal
supervision and legislation.
</P>
<P>
The system of the people's congresses has been a fundamental
political system of the country, and is playing an important role
in the strategy of ruling according to law, Li said.
</P>
<P>
The people's congresses at all levels should sum up their past
successes and failures and explore new working methods and ways
for the improvement of legislation, Li noted.
</P>
<P>
During his visit, Li stressed the supervision of government
work by the people's congresses, saying efforts must be taken to
guarantee the fairness and authority of the supervision.
</P>
<P>
Li disclosed that the NPC will send inspection teams to various
parts of the country this year, and that these teams will focus on
the implementation of five laws including the criminal procedure
law, as well as issues about which the masses are most concerned.
</P>
<P>
During his tour of Shanghai, Li also noted the importance of
deputies to the people's congresses, saying that better conditions
should be created to help the deputies play their proper roles.
</P>
