Shanghai, Fudan held an international seminar on the Song Dynasty
(960-1279) literature recently which attracted over 120
participants, at least 40 more than the number anticipated.
</P>
<P>
Some Asian countries now teach Chinese in their secondary
schools and universities, Wenhui Daily reported Monday.
</P>
<P>
