that the candidates should be politically qualified, behave well,
and be in good health.
</P>
<P>
Policemen in Beijing used to come from graduates of some
professional schools and veterans.
</P>
<P>
The candidates will be judged by an interview, paper test,
psychological test, physical examination and political examination.
The recruits will have one year on probation.  
