At the same time, a series of seminars, lectures, training
programs and information services will be held during the
exposition, he said.
</P>
<P>
The previous expositions have attracted a total of 700,000
business people and visitors from across the world and seen the
signing of nearly 2,000 high-tech and trade contracts involving a
total of 1.72 billion yuan, he added.  
